{"tid":566112,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"新年又完了 好不安","createTime":"2018-02-19T15:49:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T21:02:18.000Z","uid":143372,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eccc2d344d847b2db6a4ce0953ec94a9556cbb9f","tid":566112,"uid":143372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:49:30.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺每年一到新年就好開心 但開心過後就好不安<br />\n除左要返工讀書外 每一個新年完都代表你同長輩老人家少一個新年可以過<br />\n咁講好on9 但細細個以為好平常的新年其實唔係永恆不變 你封利是唔係永遠有得𢭃 有啲人唔係永遠有得見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人生到我呢個年紀就好似同時間競賽 希望儘早岀人頭地 成家立室 等啲老人家唔洗擔心 好彩嘅就俾佢地抱下曾孫<br />\n但又一個新年完我仲係渾渾噩噩<br />\n又少一年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知好多連登仔覺得被人問長問短好撚煩 新年志在𢭃下利是 封廿蚊仲要屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但總有人在意同錫你 好似你父母咁 <br />\n唔好成人嫌人煩 每樣野都有quota 同佢地一齊嘅日子唔係必然 尤其係老人家<br />\n新一年祝大家身體健康 團團圓圓 人生無悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n恭喜恭喜"},{"pid":"f0b1e0ee902ab0ff482290e9310a8785eeb1cad8","tid":566112,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 體育台"},{"pid":"cbba4a293d8d88052a38812a7517047e78d8057c","tid":566112,"uid":139676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bfcb9f67ebd5a1651844d38590715e0c1ff1be4","tid":566112,"uid":80183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0b1e0ee902ab0ff482290e9310a8785eeb1cad8","tid":566112,"uid":4586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 體育台"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T15:54:09.000Z","msg":"拜年刺激過藍波狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ecff88b